@startuml seq_17_save_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-17 Save Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Save Repo" as SaveRepo

User -> Frontend: Click "Save Post"
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/posts/{id}/save
Controller -> Service: Save Post (userID, postID)
Service -> PostRepo: Verify post exists
PostRepo --> Service: Post is valid

Service -> SaveRepo: Check if already saved
SaveRepo --> Service: Check result

alt Not yet saved
    Service -> SaveRepo: Create saved-post record
    SaveRepo --> Service: Record created
else Already saved
    Service -> Service: Do nothing (Idempotent)
end

Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Update bookmark icon UI
@enduml